lead_paragraph: Former Republican U.S. Defense Secretary William Cohen on Wednesday said he will likely vote for U.S. Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton in the Nov. 8 U.S. presidential election, citing her experience as secretary of state and former first lady.

headline.main: Republican Ex-Defense Secretary Cohen Backs Hillary Clinton
headline.print_headline: Republican Ex-Defense Secretary Cohen Backs Hillary Clinton
